            <p class="reveal-up text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed mb-6">
              A casement window is <strong class="text-slate-700">hinged on one side</strong> and swings outward like a door when you turn a crank handle. The single sash opens fully, directing breezes into your home and providing an unobstructed view with no meeting rail in the middle.
